name: 🏆 G9 | BRISK | RARE BIRD! 🦆
bio: Mahalo! I'm 🏆 G9 | BRISK | RARE BIRD! 🦆. I want to live in a world where people believe that one day cats will rule this planet. Sometimes I daydream of a life full of watching Stranger Things, wet food, and mocking dogs. Our friendship will be voluptuous, petulant, and full of ice cream.
